  <brief_title>Clinical Trail to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Adhesion Barrier Mediclore Versus no Treatment in Patients With Total Thyroidectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Single-blind, Multi-center, Phase III Clinical Trail to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Adhesion Barrier Mediclore Versus no Treatment in Patients With Total Thyroidectomy</official_title>
