  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A randomized, single-blind, multi-center, Phase III clinical trial to evaluate the efficacy
      and safety of adhesion barrier Mediclore versus no treatment in patients with total
      thyroidectomy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
